works.description: So, what could be the best gift for a man who has it all? German publisher teNeues goes with the amazing Aston Martin One-77 luxury car, which appears on the cover of its new book Luxury Toys for Men. Priced at $1.7 million each, the Aston Martin One-77 is an extremely special edition super car limited to only 77 units. Other luxury cars listed in the super-sized volume include the Audi R8 GT, Rolls-Royce Ghost, Jaguar XKR Special Edition
